---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Far East Metals" description="Learn about Far East Metals Development Limited - Hong Kong's aluminum industry leader since 2003. Specializing in extrusion, forging, and ingot production with a network of 100+ factories.">
  <section class="about-page">
    <div class="content-card">
      <h1>About Far East Metals</h1>
      <p class="intro">
        Founded in 2003 with its headquarters in Hong Kong, Far East Metals Development Limited stands as a prominent industry leader, specializing in aluminum extrusion, forging, and ingot production. Our primary commitment is to cultivate robust partnerships between our Chinese clientele and global customers.
      </p>

      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card content-card-inner">
          <h3>Manufacturing Network</h3>
          <p>Extensive network of over 100 factories offering comprehensive aluminum production processes</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card content-card-inner">
          <h3>Global Presence</h3>
          <p>Supporting manufacturers and distributors in establishing a formidable global presence</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card content-card-inner">
          <h3>Premium Quality</h3>
          <p>Delivering premium products and services tailored to precise specifications</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="services-section content-card-inner">
        <h2>Our Services</h2>
        <ul class="services-list">
          <li>Extruding</li>
          <li>Flat rolling</li>
          <li>Forging</li>
          <li>Deep processing</li>
          <li>Stamping</li>
          <li>Surface treatment</li>
          <li>Die Casting</li>
          <li>Heat treatment</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="services-desc">
          With our extensive manufacturing capabilities, we offer a comprehensive array of aluminum production processes to accommodate diverse requirements.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="wyeetech-section content-card-inner">
        <h2>Wyeetech Technology Limited</h2>
        <p>
          <a href="https://www.wyeetech.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Wyeetech Technology Limited</a>, a National High-Tech Enterprise and subsidiary of Far East Metals Development Limited, specializes in precision forging and extruding. This further contributes to our unwavering commitment to excellence in the industry.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="brochure-section content-card-inner">
        <a href="/brochure.pdf" class="brochure-link" download="Far_East_Metals_Brochure.pdf">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg>
          <span>Download Our Company Brochure</span>
          <span class="brochure-size">PDF, 3.6 MB</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding: 100px 20px 60px;
  }

  .intro {
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .feature-card {
    padding: 30px;
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .services-section {
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .services-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 8px 30px;
    list-style: none;
    margin: 15px 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .services-list li {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    padding: 6px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200, 200, 200, 0.3);
  }

  .services-desc {
    margin-top: 15px;
  }

  .wyeetech-section {
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .wyeetech-section a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .wyeetech-section a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .brochure-section {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .brochure-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 12px;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 18px 24px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 10px;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .brochure-link:hover {
    background: #d4891a;
  }

  .brochure-size {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .services-list {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .brochure-link {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 6px;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .brochure-link svg {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
    }

    .brochure-size {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
  }
</style>
